[[File:ITOInterrogatorDroid-CGSWG.png|thumb|right|270px|An IT-O interrogation droid]]
'''Interrogation droids''', also referred to as '''interrogator droids''' or '''torture droids''', were [[droid]]s designed to coax sensitive information out of an individual by [[Torture|inflicting extreme pain]] upon them. Some models, such as the [[IT-O interrogation droid]], used [[mind probe]]s to torture their victims.<ref name="ANH">{{Film|IV}}</ref> They often tormented fellow droids as well.<ref name="EP">{{TCW|Evil Plans}}</ref><ref name="RotJ">{{Film|VI}}</ref> Torture droids often had sadistic personalities, seemingly enjoying the suffering they caused others.<ref name="TC" />

Interrogator droids were a common sight in [[Confederacy of Independent Systems|Separatist]] [[prison]]s during the [[Clone Wars]].<ref name="TC" /><ref name="TSW">{{TCW|The Soft War}}</ref> They could also be found in [[Imperial Military|Imperial military]] installations during the [[Imperial Era|reign]] of the [[Galactic Empire]].<ref name="ANH" /> These droids also found their way into the hands of [[crime lord]]s such as [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure|Jabba]] the [[Hutt]], who had a torture chamber located in the bowels of his [[Boba Fett's Palace|palace]].<ref name="RotJ" /> A torture droid named [[J0-N0]] worked for the [[bounty hunter]] [[Cad Bane]].<ref name="EP" /> Nearly thirty [[Standard year|years]] after the [[Battle of Endor]], a [[IT-000 interrogator droid|new model]] of interrogator droid was utilized by the [[First Order]] under the command of [[Ben Solo|Kylo Ren]].<ref name="TFA interrogator DB">{{Databank|first-order-interrogator-droid|First Order Interrogator Droid}}</ref>

